value: Breeds in the southern part of the Iberian Peninsula, lower Danube and southern Russia to Persia and Transcaspia; Africa from Algeria to Cape Colony; Madagascar. Straggles after breeding north to the British Isles and Germany and to the eastern Atlantic islands. Migratory in Europe.
